screen_desc: The screenshot shows the Uber app interface. At the top, there is a search bar for entering a pickup point and a button to set the pickup time to "Now." Below the search bar, there are two promotional banners. The first banner on a green background asks, "Want better pick-ups?" with an illustration of a person looking through binoculars. The second banner on a light purple background says, "Ready? Then let’s roll. Ride with Uber" with an image of a person opening a car door. At the bottom of the screen, there is a navigation bar with icons for Home, Services, Activity, and Account. The time displayed at the top left is 3:06 PM, and the battery is fully charged at 100%.
